,Recommended,312010,20049061,"Posted: 28 December, 2015",all,CaptainCardsworth,"Why is there no ""Meh"" button.  It's neither good nor bad.  It's just average.It's Fun if you're looking to kill a little bit of time.  Feels more like a Flash game you'd find online than a game you have to buy though.  Don't pay more than a $1 for it.The ""story"" is that your dad (pa) is killed by an ostrich and you go on a murderous rampage to avenge his death.Repetitive gameplay but fun atmosphere.  You collect money for each bird you kill and can pick up coins for bonus money.  Use the money to buy upgrades that you'll need as birds become more numerous as you go.Not a hard game, but not ""super"" easy either.  Worth a buck, but only takes an hour or so to complete the game (less if you're good and don't die)."
